ESSENCE' 1.0
given n_ticks : int(1..n)
letting INDEX be domain int(1..n_ticks), 
	ARRAY_INDEX be domain int(0..(n_ticks-1))
find x:bool, y : bool, xxx : matrix indexed by [INDEX] of INDEX, 
   yyy : matrix indexed by [INDEX] of INDEX
minimising max(ruler)
such that x =y,
          forall i,j, k : INDEX . xxx[i] = yyy[j] + k
